=== 評價 ===
電影上映後，獲得了兩極的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度85%，基於291條評論，平均分為7.2/10，而觀眾評價僅獲得45%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hail_caesar_2009/ |title=Hail, Caesar! (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124111617/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hail_caesar_2009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分72，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hail-caesar! |title=Hail, Caesar! reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205074238/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hail-caesar! |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾從A+至F間給了「C-」的平均分數<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/pride-prejudice-and-zombies-hail-caesar-the-choice-weekend-box-office-1201697018/ |title=‘Kung Fu Panda 3’ Pummeling ‘Caesar’, ‘Zombies’ & ‘The Choice’ At Weekend B.O. |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206083429/http://deadline.com/2016/02/pride-prejudice-and-zombies-hail-caesar-the-choice-weekend-box-office-1201697018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，儘管收穫多數影評人的好評，但普遍不受觀眾青睞。

=== 票房 ===
《凱薩萬歲！》於2016年2月5日在北美與《[[傲慢與偏見與殭屍_(電影)|傲慢與偏見與殭屍]]》、《{{link-en|愛情的選擇|The Choice (2016 film)}}》同時上映。週四晚上獲得54萬3000美元的票房<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/pride-prejudice-and-zombies-hail-caesar-the-choice-weekend-box-office-1201697018/ |title=Moviegoers Begin To ‘Hail, Caesar!’ & Walk To ‘Zombies’ On Thursday Night |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206083429/http://deadline.com/2016/02/pride-prejudice-and-zombies-hail-caesar-the-choice-weekend-box-office-1201697018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

